verbose_text: Nrf2 is released from Keap1 under conditions of oxidative stress or other potential damage and then translocates to the nucleus, where it binds to antioxidant response element (ARE) sequences, leading to the transcriptional activation of anti-apoptotic genes, including HO-1.
